OL,3,CGPs vote in favour of 'unprecedented'
OL,4,Ccollective action over funding dispute
OL,6,FGPs across Northern Ireland are to
OL,7,Freduce the "unfunded work" they carry
OL,8,Fout, the British Medical Association
OL,9,F(BMA) has said.
OL,11,FOn Monday, the BMA announced GPs will
OL,12,Fcontinue the action until they receive
OL,13,Fan improved funding package from the
OL,14,FDepartment of Health.
OL,16,FThe BMA said measures taken by doctors
OL,17,Fwould include limiting patient
OL,18,Fconsultations to a maximum of 25 per
OL,19,Fday and switching off medical
OL,20,Foptimisation software.
