OL,6,FThe union said GPs remained committed
OL,7,F"to minimising the impact on patients".
OL,9,FIn May, Health Minister Mike Nesbitt
OL,10,Fsaid he would implement a funding
OL,11,Fcontract for GP surgeries, despite it
OL,12,Fhaving already been rejected by
OL,13,Fdoctors.
OL,15,FThe minister had offered a package of
OL,16,F#9.5 million in additional core
OL,17,Ffunding for services for GPs.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@fO]
