OL,6,FBut the BMA said its members had
OL,7,Foverwhelmingly rejected the 2025/26
OL,8,FGeneral Medical Services (GMS)
OL,9,Fcontract offered by the Department of
OL,10,FHealth.
OL,12,FAt the time, Mr Nesbitt said that the
OL,13,FBMA had asked for an extra #80
OL,14,Fmillion, but said this would be used
OL,15,Fto deliver "more of the same", citing
OL,16,Fconcerns about access to surgeries for
OL,17,Fpatients.
OL,19,FThe BMA has raised concerns over
OL,20,Funderfunding of practices, workload
OL,21,Fand staff shortages.
