OL,6,F"Patients are not the focus of our
OL,7,Fdispute; it is the department's
OL,8,Fapproach that is forcing us into
OL,9,Faction."
OL,11,FThe BMA said measures being
OL,12,Fimplemented include limiting patient
OL,13,Fconsultations to the recommended
OL,14,Fmaximum of 25 per day.
