OL,3,CGPs vote in favour of 'unprecedented'
OL,4,Ccollective action over funding dispute
OL,6,FIt also said measures would include
OL,7,F"stopping completing unfunded
OL,8,Fpaperwork requests" including patient
OL,9,Fregistration paperwork verification
OL,10,Fand switching off medical optimisation
OL,11,Fsoftware and GPs instead using
OL,12,Fclinical judgement when prescribing.
OL,14,FDr O'Hagan added: "The collective
OL,15,Faction undertaken by GPs is a clear
OL,16,Fcall for the health minister to
OL,17,Frecognise the severity of the
OL,18,Fsituation and to take immediate and
OL,19,Fdecisive action.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@SO]vD@SOU
