OL,6,FShe added: "Current funding levels are
OL,7,Finsufficient to meet patient needs,
OL,8,Fand increased investment is required
OL,9,Fto maintain safe, high-quality care.
OL,11,F"Patients deserve and need a properly
OL,12,Ffunding service that is sustainable
OL,13,Fand retains quality of patient care.
OL,15,F"It is vital that immediate, targeted
OL,16,Faction is taken to address current
OL,17,Ffunding gaps and resource challenges
OL,18,Fin general practice."
OL,20,FThe Department of Health has been
OL,21,Fapproached for comment.
