OL,6,FShe added: "It is not for RCGPNI to
OL,7,Fget involved in contractual
OL,8,Fnegotiations between the BMA's NIGPC
OL,9,Fand the Department of Health, nor to
OL,10,Finfluence any decision making about
OL,11,Fcollective action, but it is
OL,12,Fdisappointing that negotiations did
OL,13,Fnot reopen, and we have arrived at the
OL,14,Funprecedented position where
OL,15,Fcollective action from GPs will
OL,16,Fcommence imminently.
