OL,6,F"Absolutely no GP will want to
OL,7,Frestrict the services they provide for
OL,8,Ftheir patients ` and it needs to be
OL,9,Fmade clear that GPs and their teams
OL,10,Fwill still be working extremely hard
OL,11,Fto care for our patients.
OL,13,F"There are many aspects of what GPs
OL,14,Fprovide that go well beyond the
OL,15,Fcontractual requirements they are
OL,16,Funder and what they receive funding
OL,17,Ffor, and this additional workload and
OL,18,Fthe goodwill of the GPs delivering it,
OL,19,Fhave been taken for granted for too
OL,20,Flong."
